rea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1584417392070-1702486999_image_8_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/89448a3f70ee1cb0.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1584417392070-1702486999_image_8_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/89448a3f70ee1cb0.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/89448a3f70ee1cb0.jpg\" data-width=\"3024\" data-height=\"4032\" width=\"3024\" height=\"4032\" data-attachment-id=\"IdqP9x0RoY3CLg21NaX-KJDYMQFQ\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>나무 수저로&nbsp;뜰 때&nbsp;아주 부드러운 경옥고의 질감이 전달되나요? <br></span><span>맛을 보면 아주 부드럽고 달콤하고, 약간은 쌉싸름한! 제대로 된 경옥고의 풍미를 느낄 수 있습니다. </span><span><br></span><span></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>경옥고를 먹을 때는 단지 뚜껑을 열고 수저로 떠서 먹거나 따뜻한 물에 타 먹는데, 아무래도 번거롭죠. 특히 외부에서 시간을 많이 보내야 하는 경우에는 더욱 그렇습니다. <br></span><span>그래서 경옥고를 가공하여 짜서 먹을 수 있게 포장했습니다. <br></span><span>너무너무 편하겠죠!!</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1584417392070-1702486999_image_9_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/64dd89192543d1b9.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1584417392070-1702486999_image_9_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/64dd89192543d1b9.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/64dd89192543d1b9.jpg\" data-width=\"4032\" data-height=\"3024\" width=\"4032\" height=\"3024\" data-attachment-id=\"IFhQgwr0khw4WAXm2pPXnM1jWqWw\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>짜먹는 경옥고는 하루 한 포를 간편하게 짜서 먹으면 됩니다. <br></span><span>주머니 속에, 가방속에 편하게 들고다니다가 편하게 쭉~ <br></span><span></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>이번엔 이수한의원에서 처방하는 공진단을 소개할께요</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>먼저 식약처에서 인증하는 정품 사향으로 만든 '사향공진단'입니다. <br></span><span>식약처에서 인증하는 사향은 아래 사진처럼 원통형 케이스에 담겨 있어요. <br></span><span>포장은 고급스런 나무박스를 사용합니다. <br></span><span>고마운 분께 선물하기에도 아주 좋습니다. </span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_imageStrip imageStrip3 default \">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-extend\">\n        <div class=\"se_viewArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\n                <div class=\"se_imageStripView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_mediaArea\">\n                                                <div class=\"se_imageStripArea\" style=\"width:40.0%;\">\n                       